What you need to know:

The first eight in the 4x100m, 4x400m and 4x400m races shall automatically qualify for the Olympics Games and if the country already qualified through the World Athletics Championships in Doha 2019, the remaining places will be allocated to the World Athletics Performance lists of June 2021.The first 10 in the 4x100m and 4x400m and first 12 in the Mixed 4x400m will automatically qualify for the World Championships in Oregon next year.